<p class="s">sphaers, sphears: both old form of 'spheres'</p>

<p>5) Stephen Sachs has written a <a href="http://www.stevesachs.com/jumbler.cgi">CGI script to jumble text</a>. Simply enter your text into the www page and press the button for a newly scrambled text.</p>



